## AI Models or you can specify which AI models you want to use by setting the `AI_MODELS` environment variable in your `.env` file. The available models are:
# OPENAI_API_KEY=
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=
# GOOGLE_API_KEY=
# OPENROUTER_API_KEY=
AI_MODELS="gpt-5.5,claude-sonnet-4,gemini-2.5-pro,llama-4-maverick"

# NVD API
NVD_API_KEY="your_nvd_api_key_here"

# CISA KEV
CISA_KEV_URL="https://www.cisa.gov/sites/default/files/feeds/known_exploited_vulnerabilities.json"

# EPSS
EPSS_API_URL="https://api.first.org/data/v1/epss"